<h3 id="description">Description</h3>
<p>Ligatation of multiple phased BCF/VCF files into a single whole chromosome file. GLIMPSE2 is run in chunks that are ligated into chromosome-wide files maintaining the phasing.</p>

<h3 id="usage">Usage</h3>
